dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Juneau County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Juneau County, Wisconsin in 2018 and includes the layers 'Juneau_Roads_2018' and 'Juneau_ROW_2018'. Roads: [Roads data contain the centerlines of all the roads in the county. They are coded by class being: 5 - Interstates, 4 - US Highways, 3 - State Highways, 2 - County Trunk Roads, 1 - Town/Local Roads and 0 - Private Roads, Trails or Alleys. They also have an address range assigned to them with a right and left to and from range, the centerlines broken down into segments with what community (zipcode) they are in, and also what emergency zone (ESN) they fall in.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2019. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2018. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2019.
